yarn add — adds packages to your project.

-D or --dev — adds these packages as development dependencies (used only during development, not in production).

typescript — the TypeScript language compiler and tools.

@types/node — TypeScript type definitions for Node.js, which provide type information for Node's built-in modules like fs, http, etc., enabling better code completion and error checking.


